{"tid":770312,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【加息鳥】花旗調升H按封頂息至2.35厘 每月或供多250元","createTime":"2018-08-07T03:47:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-07T04:08:43.000Z","uid":48974,"like":9,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"71d1fb5d4c52d58f6241734c5acb2ec2c14d7339","tid":770312,"uid":48974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T03:47:07.000Z","msg":"因應港元資金成本上升，再有銀行調高H按封頂息率，花旗宣佈，H按計劃為一個月拆息（H）加1.4厘，封頂息率為最優惠利率（P）減2.9厘，而花旗P為5.25厘，即實際為2.35厘，在現時一個月拆息持續高企下，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">等於供樓客須多付利息0.1厘</span>。<br />\n<br />\n反而P按計劃似乎更有着數，其實際利率為P-3厘，即等於2.25厘，在1個月拆息高漲時，P按反而更有着數。<br />\n<br />\n以市民參與H按買600萬樓為例，首期為2成，分攤30年歸還，假設利率為2.35厘，每月供款為18594元，假設利率是2.25厘，每月供款則為18348元，微<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>升250元</strong></span>。<br />\n<br />\n花旗指，會不時檢視按揭息率，並因應市場情況作出調整，是次調整按息利率是因為要平衡資金成本上升的壓力，提升銀行風險管理。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20180807&amp;s=7015342&amp;a=58532846\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180807%26s%3D7015342%26a%3D58532846&d=HyTeR31y2n6e9uAjay0mD%2FiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=7204909d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180807%26s%3D7015342%26a%3D58532846&h=e4ca895c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20180807&amp;s=7015342&amp;a=58532846</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 樓爆將至<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 繼續gogogo"},{"pid":"293af731fcebfd207ddf700d41a0499193f79a34","tid":770312,"uid":511,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T03:54:42.000Z","msg":"Mola mola<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"960fd3d5d99893126f2e1b2e366fae8badd3e12b","tid":770312,"uid":122377,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T03:57:03.000Z","msg":"以前 <br />\n樓平息貴<br />\n依家 <br />\n樓貴息平 <br />\n<br />\n但當之後 息都唔再平既時候<br />\n真係唔知香港樓價重點橕落去 <br />\n<br />\n我知今次加得0.1厘 好少 <br />\n食少餐飯都係到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但加息係周期黎 依家岩岩開始姐 <br />\n唔洗心急"},{"pid":"544ee6f5ee9d8625267b885bdca5839b3440dd20","tid":770312,"uid":25641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T04:00:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a57fecb4cd0140c616ea565fd166cecb2c85025e","tid":770312,"uid":21917,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T04:08:43.000Z","msg":"供得起呢個價既 食餐飯都應該係呢個數兩倍啦"}]}